title: Master Your Reactions
itunes:title: Master Your Reactions
description:
Episode 137 - A big mistake that people make is identifying themselves as the reaction that they most frequently use. For instance, people say they are emotional, lazy or stressed out. They are NOT that emotion, they just frequently use it so it is dangerous identifying themselves as that reaction. In this episode I dive into this topic and tell you how to take the next step in mastering your mindset.
